    <string name="kosail">Made by kosail</string>

    <string name="about_this_app">Details about this app</string>

    <string name="tribute_zero">Aria is a handcrafted tribute to Blanket, a wonderful Linux ambient sounds app, originally created by Rafael Mardojai, part of the GNOME Desktop Circle.</string>

    <string name="tribute_one">Though beautiful, it was only for Linux. I rebuilt it from scratch for many other devices, because I wanted that my mom had better sleep without spending too much mobile data on YouTube videos.</string>

    <string name="tribute_two">
        Like the original, Aria has no accounts, no ads, no clutter. Just nature’s sounds. Mix them, adjust them, let them fade away as you rest or work.
    </string>

    <string name="donations_text">
        If you enjoy Aria and find it useful, you can support its development with a voluntary donation.

        Your support helps keep the project free, open-source, and actively maintained.
    </string>
